summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 23E, Page 78 of the official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property located at the southwest corner of North East 43rd Street and Brooklyn Avenue North East from Multiple Residence High Density (RMH 350) Zone to Community Business (BC) Zone. (Petition of Baxter C. Felch, C.F. 289693).
